{"tid":1859283,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護罷工危機[危與機]","createTime":"2020-02-03T07:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T08:09:58.000Z","uid":260866,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"efea33b819a60c09161454f90c6b5d0d0642049b","tid":1859283,"uid":260866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T07:22:05.000Z","msg":"根本唔係政治訴求, 大家係咪傻L左, 咁多連登仔女連埋政治黎講... <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當左係政治訴求既現象<br />\n1. 今次醫護罷工五大訴求<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔係</strong></span>政治訴求! 只係為公共安全, 所以左報紅媒都出黎講野<br />\n2. 唔多人去支持醫護罷工, 大部份人都係無參與係其中, 繼續自己生活<br />\n3. 其他工會雖然有行動, 但係大眾情感上focus左落醫護到<br />\n影響(危):<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. (如果迫到政府封關)同區選差不多, 會令抗爭熱度再次減低, 街頭抗爭會更加危險(利申: 非民意撚), 危險就增加被捕風險, 亦少左人出黎<br />\n2. 本來6月至11月都係非常團結, 由區選之後好多人開始變左等其他人做野, 開始懶, 因為組織左工會, (題外話, 大家入左工會未, 未入既同我), 其實呢個政府淨係醫護罷工佢地都未必跪低, 要各行各界響應, (<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>日期越後越好, 最好係醫護罷工day 4, 因為民怨更高, 而且大家口罩庫存更少, 罷工意慾增加, 但係相對罷工殺傷都係減少</strong></span></span>)<br />\n3. 唔同工會行動得唔到大眾支持, 變得心理上可有可無, 影響下一次政治性大罷工的成功率, 所以至少要有最簡單既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>全民聯署支持</strong></span>。<br />\n講下有咩機啦:<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 民怨增加, 黃藍一齊set road board都見到, 要把握機會, 慢慢<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">突破同溫層</span></strong>。 最簡單, 在家中諗方法, 最緊要唔好硬碰硬, 搵方法入佢中路, 或者動之以情先, 如果佢唔講道理既話, 慢慢滲入本土意識, 即係香港政府要優先考慮香港人<br />\n2. 叫<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非升級</span></span></strong>, 之前好多初變黃(我老母佔中係藍, 而家黃左)既家長可能都未必改變到習慣, 罷鐵/食黃店, 今次肺炎風波係一個好方法比佢地睇清楚黨鐵其實真係做得好差, (連年加價, 壞車, 壞信號, 月台沉降, etc. ); 同埋黃店不等於政治色彩, 佢地的確係有<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>良心</strong></span></span>好多, (上網search, 大把可能連你都未聽過)<br />\n3. 多一個藉口叫政府<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">高官下台</span></span></strong>, 如果疫情真係爆發, 至少要拉到班高官落黎, 唔拉落黎其實<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">會有清算風險</span></span></strong>, 所以先咁需要要求佢地問責下台!! 陳_始, 林奠, etc!!<br />\n<br />\n而家可以做既行動:<br />\n計劃聯署支持不同各界人士罷工!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n👊🏻香港全民議政會⚖️<br />\n※全民議政，以民制權※<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KYc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=40ba225b\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a> <br />\n<br />\n幫手推, P牌推唔郁! 光復香港, 時代革命! <br />\n康復香港! 時代抗疫! <br />\n好人一生平安"},{"pid":"71e1a400e673be476abd8e395b729e6e72bcc1fc","tid":1859283,"uid":260866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T07:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yPm9phf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyPm9phf.jpg&h=faa1d8cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/brfKdaB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbrfKdaB.jpg&h=280f95ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2oWOJW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2oWOJW.jpg&h=2f85b38d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kh9i13X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkh9i13X.jpg&h=76fc5065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4WMUAoX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4WMUAoX.jpg&h=407943be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X4SpdaD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX4SpdaD.jpg&h=0d28c13f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj